message: It's a fact that Jayley Woo has been addressing him as 大神 even before his death. Please do not erase this. And she is indeed a stalker and a milker. I'm staying facts, not rumors.
Everyone knows and recognizes his death date as 23 Jan, although his official date of death is 24 Jan.
/* Impact and aftermath */Pang was also at fault for not following safety protocols. You can't make these two guys take full responsibility either.
The news of his death was made public on 23 Jan, so it should be his official death date.
